source: TEXT_CMNGSCWEEKLYLOTUNLOCKTALK_00105_LOTTERY00105_000_000<tab>Have you come to try the Jumbo Cactpot, <var 08 E905 ((miss)) ((sir)) /var>? The lady at the center of that counter will help you get started.
